text: Tarapara'o era mithya pratipanna karala. Sutaram take ebam tara sathe naukaya yara chila tadera ke bamciye niyechi ebam yathasthane abada karechi. Ara taderake dubiye diyechi yara amara kathake mithya pratipanna kareche. Sutaram laksya kara, kemana parinati ghateche tadera yaderake bhiti pradarsana kara hayechila.
